33:36.849 --> 33:38.682
Welcome home, TK.

33:38.833 --> 33:41.518
(bright music playing)

33:47.526 --> 33:48.841
You know, you...

33:48.935 --> 33:52.011
You are the world's
biggest control freak, right?

33:52.031 --> 33:54.847
Yeah, yeah, yeah.
It's okay. You love it.

33:54.867 --> 33:57.200
You love it.
It's okay. It's okay.

33:57.644 --> 33:58.535
(grunts)

34:01.206 --> 34:02.614
You guys ready to meet
your little cousin?

34:02.708 --> 34:03.765
EVIE AND IZZY: Yeah.

34:03.858 --> 34:06.043
<i> Tranquilas.</i>
She might be sleeping.

34:06.270 --> 34:08.453
Oh, friend, I wish.

34:08.547 --> 34:10.297
Come say hey, girls.

34:11.533 --> 34:12.883
It's all right.
She won't bite.

34:13.034 --> 34:14.200
Oh, she bites.

34:14.294 --> 34:15.886
But she saves that
just for her mama.

34:16.037 --> 34:17.962
Aw, she's so cute!

34:18.115 --> 34:20.448
Thank you.
Now this is Evie and Izzy.

34:20.542 --> 34:22.893
