out for you your whole life,

34:23.044 --> 34:24.561
so you gotta do
what they say, okay?

34:24.788 --> 34:26.121
We'll be nice, we promise.

34:26.256 --> 34:27.713
We brought her something.

34:27.733 --> 34:29.307
I see. What is this?

34:29.459 --> 34:31.976
A penguin. Because she
was born in the snow.

34:32.071 --> 34:34.071
Y'all are so sweet.
Thank you so much.

34:34.298 --> 34:35.721
-I thought of it.
-IZZY: No, you did not.

34:35.741 --> 34:36.907
-EVIE: Did so.
-I'm the one

34:37.134 --> 34:39.484
who just did the report
on the emperor penguins.

34:39.578 --> 34:41.136
-EVIE: So what?
-TOMMY: Ladies, enough.

34:41.229 --> 34:43.580
Y'all did the right thing
just startin' with one.

34:43.731 --> 34:46.249
Oh, she's beautiful. Aw.

34:46.401 --> 34:48.493
Yeah, she's lucky.
She favors her mama.

34:48.587 --> 34:51.237
Oh, yeah, well, I see plenty
of you in there, Juddy.

34:51.331 --> 34:52.238
Oh, my goodness.

34:52.424 --> 34:53.757
All right, time to
take your godchild.

34:53.908 --> 34:55.258
What took you so long?

34:55.410 --> 34:58.136
My goodness.
(speaking Spanish)

35:01.082 --> 35:02.915
Oh! Now have y'all decided

35:02.935 --> 35:04.643
what you're gonna name
this miracle baby?

35:05.662 --> 35:07.479
(wistful music playing)

35:12.111 --> 35:14.361
Tommy, we wanted
to name her Charlie.

35:16.006 --> 35:17.781
EVIE: Charlie's a boy's name.

35:17.932 --> 35:20.266
Hey, now.

35:20.285 --> 35:22.602
IZZY: Sounds like
our father's name.

35:22.696 --> 35:24.162
Mm-hmm.

35:25.958 --> 35:27.499
GRACE: Now we, um...

35:28.794 --> 35:30.961
we just wanted
to honor him, T.

35:31.188 --> 35:33.021
We don't wanna
overstep in any way.

35:33.114 --> 35:35.114
Yeah, if it's, if it's
uncomfortable or anything,

35:35.134 --> 35:37.134
you know,
we ain't married to it, so...

35:38.862 --> 35:40.262
I like it.

35:41.122 --> 35:42.697
Yeah. Do you like it?

35:42.716 --> 35:43.807
(coos)

35:44.034 --> 35:45.559
I like it very much.

35:49.055 --> 35:51.148
FOREMAN:
All right, Marty. Lower it down.

35:51.817 --> 35:53.400
Go more. More.

35:54.895 --> 35:56.528
Can't believe it's finally over.

35:58.048 --> 36:00.640
MARJAN: Hey, at least
we went down swinging.

36:00.659 --> 36:03.160
Thank you
for fighting for the 126...

36:03.996 --> 36:05.662
and for me.

36:06.999 --> 36:08.665
It's been a pleasure
working with you, Marjan.

36:08.816 --> 36:09.908
You, too.

36:10.060 --> 36:11.893
I have never had
as much fun on the job

36:11.986 --> 36:13.670
as in your house, Cap.

36:13.897 --> 36:15.172
That's very kind of you to say.

36:15.323 --> 36:17.582
FOREMAN:
All right, Marty. Lower it down.

36:17.734 --> 36:18.675
Little more.

36:18.902 --> 36:20.343
It's good.

36:21.162 --> 36:22.995
