and the building that it's in.

40:20.568 --> 40:21.325
(laughter)

40:21.420 --> 40:23.569
-Red, red!
-(Mateo muttering)

40:23.588 --> 40:26.297
(overlapping chatter)

40:28.318 --> 40:30.427
Hey, hippie. You wanna hold her?

40:31.171 --> 40:32.987
Uh, that's all right.

40:33.080 --> 40:34.431
