you have on most people, but...

40:36.435 --> 40:39.352
she's gotta get
used to you sometime.

40:39.938 --> 40:41.354
Come on.

40:42.832 --> 40:44.724
All right. Come here, you.

40:44.834 --> 40:45.608
Come on.

40:45.760 --> 40:46.926
Oh-oh.

40:46.945 --> 40:48.594
Oh, don't do it.

40:48.613 --> 40:49.671
Don't cry.

40:49.764 --> 40:51.364
(laughter)

40:52.767 --> 40:54.859
BILLY: Hell.

40:54.953 --> 40:56.694
That's a future
fire chief right there.

40:56.846 --> 40:58.413
JUDD: Oh, Billy!

40:59.958 --> 41:01.941
So what do you think?
It's still homey, right?

41:02.035 --> 41:03.442
I didn't go too far
on the remodel.

41:03.536 --> 41:05.853
What are you talking about?
It looks exactly the same, Dad.

41:05.872 --> 41:07.112
Are you out of your mind?

41:07.132 --> 41:10.541
The subway tile on
the backsplash is new, isn't it?

41:10.694 --> 41:11.784
Thank you, Carlos.

41:11.803 --> 41:13.044
Always wanted
to get rid of that.

41:13.196 --> 41:15.597
