kinda worth it.

41:17.659 --> 41:19.184
(Owen sighs)

41:20.537 --> 41:21.478
(mouths): Hi.

41:21.813 --> 41:23.646
Mom?

41:23.798 --> 41:24.814
Is she really here?

41:25.041 --> 41:26.541
She's late, but she's here.

41:26.559 --> 41:30.061
