more fun to surprise you.

41:35.235 --> 41:37.660
-Hi, Carlos.
-Hi, good to see you, Gwyneth.

41:37.812 --> 41:39.162
-Oh, my goodness.
-Hi! Hi.

41:39.313 --> 41:39.996
